Subject: [EVP-ITC]



 These are direct from the system output speaker, the speaker that will
provide the raw audio output for this box. There seems to be more static on
the AM band tonight, part of that is cuz I think this board has more RF gain
at the antenna then the previous board. It probably depends on the type of
core I used for the coil, and since they are from the junk box, I have no
idea what the permeability rating is for these cores. The core being a
ferrite bobbin that I wind the coil on. 

 Frank-S

